    <p>We want these couple of days to be truly enjoyable for everyone.  Attendees, speakers, sponsors and volunteers must respect the <a href="http://jsconf.com/codeofconduct.html">JSConf Code of Conduct</a>. If anything happens that you feel we should know about, please contact one of the organizers.</p>
