<p>For the <a href="./schedule">conference main track</a> we invite <a href="./speakers">16 speakers</a>. We do not have a CFP and our <a href="./policies">policy</a> is that speakers at the conference get paid for their travel and accommodation. We do not sell speaker slots and we do not accept sales pitches masked as presentations.
